  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To test the value of preoperatively performed urodynamics with regard to outcome of surgery
      for stress urinary incontinence (SUI) and to examine whether not performing urodynamics
      preoperatively is more cost effective than performing urodynamics preoperatively using the
      non-inferiority assumption.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
